# Hi Tech Software — Windsurf Rules

## Project
Service Management System for Hi Tech Engineering, Kottayam Kerala.
Client: Hi Tech Engineering
Developer: Supportta Solutions Private Limited
Stack: Next.js 16.1.6 App Router, Supabase, TypeScript,
TailwindCSS 4, TanStack Query, Zustand, React Hook Form, Zod,
React 19.2.3, Turbopack enabled by default.
Flutter apps: hitech_admin and hitech_technician.
Monorepo: npm workspaces + Turborepo. Node >= 22.

## Folder Structure
- Web app: /web
- Admin Flutter: /hitech_admin
- Technician Flutter: /hitech_technician
- Migrations: /supabase/migrations
- Docs: /doc
- Work log: /doc/WORK_LOG.md

## Architecture — NEVER VIOLATE
UI (app/) → Hook (hooks/) → Service (modules/) → Repository (repositories/) → Supabase
- Never call Supabase from UI or hooks directly
- Never put business logic in repositories
- All forms use React Hook Form + Zod
- All server state uses TanStack Query
- Pages must stay under 150 lines
- Always use ProtectedComponent for role-based UI

## Supabase Client Rules
- Browser components → lib/supabase/client.ts
- API routes → lib/supabase/server.ts
- Cron and admin → lib/supabase/admin.ts
- Middleware → lib/supabase/middleware.ts
- NEVER use browser client in API routes

## Roles
- super_admin — full access
- office_staff — subjects, customers, billing
- stock_manager — inventory, stock, digital bag
- technician — own jobs only via mobile

## Database Rules
- Always use get_my_role() in RLS — migrations 017+
- Before 017 use current_user_role() — never change old migrations
- Check AGENTS.md for latest migration number before creating new one
- Always IF NOT EXISTS on indexes
- Soft delete only — never hard delete
- Financial records immutable — never update, only reverse

## Pricing Rules
- MRP always inclusive of 18% GST
- Base price = MRP / 1.18
- GST = MRP - base price
- Discount per product line before GST split
- WAC auto-updates on every stock entry
- Never manually calculate GST — always MRP / 1.18

## Business Rules
- Bag capacity = 50 items per technician per day
- Attendance ON before 10:30 AM, auto OFF midnight
- Subject number unique per brand or per dealer
- AMC cannot overlap — new starts after previous ends
- Variance auto-deducted from payout
- MRP updates automatically from latest stock entry
- Selling price never below MRP
- Status values always lowercase — never uppercase

## Error Handling — Three Layers Always
- Repository — catch DB error, throw with context
- Service — catch repo error, add business context
- Hook — catch service error, show Sonner toast
- UI — show error state, never raw Supabase errors
- Success: { success: true, data: T }
- Error: { success: false, error: string, code: string }

## Code Quality
- TypeScript strict — no any types ever
- No console.log in production
- No inline styles — TailwindCSS only
- No hardcoded strings — use constants
- No SELECT * in production queries
- All monetary values rounded to 2 decimal places
- Explicit types on all filter and reduce callbacks

## Performance
- List queries paginated max 20 per page
- Search debounced 300ms minimum
- Reports use materialized views not raw tables
- Always show loading skeleton — never blank screen

## Security
- Never expose service role key in client code
- Never in NEXT_PUBLIC_ variables
- Validate role on server in every API route
- Validate input with Zod on server always


